title: ring of roses
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

While wearing this ring, you can cause a single rose to grow and appear in your hand up to three times per day. The stem is 1 foot long, and has small, dull thorns. The flower is odorless and blooms in a color of your choice, but withers and turns to dust after 24 hours.

